    "The first block has 32 filters, while the subsequent blocks have 64, 128, and 256 filters, respectively.",
    "Additionally, dropout layers and max pooling follow each block.",
    "The input shape of the CNN model is (x, y, 3), where x and y are the width and height of the resized images, respectively.",
    "The input to the CNN branch is also resized from 50 x 50 pixels to 32 x 32 pixels.",
    "On the other hand, the EfficientNetV2B3 [29] architecture has 24 layers, including 22 convolutional layers, one fully connected layer, and 1 Softmax layer."
